FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774905063
OL,3,CTumour mutation mapping could boost
OL,4,Ctargeted cancer therapies
OL,6,FCatherine Hart, chief executive of
OL,7,FTarget Ovarian Cancer, said: "These
OL,8,Ffindings have the power to transform
OL,9,Ftreatment and, ultimately, improve
OL,10,Fthousands of women's chances of
OL,11,Fsurvival."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,26,@oD@^OUsD@JO]
